				}
			]
			title: "Electrum Alloy"
			subtitle: "Smelt Electrum in the Foundry \u2014 key alloy for advanced circuits and mid-tier machine components."
			x: 14.0d
			y: 0.0d
		}
		{
			dependencies: ["E01A"]
			description: [
				"The §eCentrifuge§r is Oritech's chemical separator \u2014 it spins materials to sort them by density and produces refined intermediate products."
				""
				"§7Key outputs:§r"
				"§7Uranium Ore§r \u2192 Uranium Clumps \u2192 §eUranium Dust§r \u2192 §ePlutonium Dust§r (via Centrifuge cascade)"
				"§7Mineral Slurry§r (from water cooling) \u2192 §eRaw materials§r"
				"§7Crude Oil§r \u2192 fuel fractions via Refinery chain"
				""
				"§7Power note:§r The Centrifuge is power-hungry. Ensure you have a reliable multi-generator setup before running it continuously \u2014 it will stall weaker power setups."
			]
