		{
			dependencies: ["E01B"]
			description: [
				"The §eAssembler§r is Oritech's automated crafting machine \u2014 it automatically crafts items from stored inputs using a defined recipe."
				""
				"§7How it works:§r Right-click to open the GUI and place a target item in the recipe slot. It reads the recipe and continuously crafts it from connected inventories."
				""
				"§7Factory potential:§r Chain multiple Assemblers \u2014 the first produces components that the next consumes to build more complex items. Combined with a storage network (Refined Storage or Applied Energistics), the Assembler forms the backbone of a fully automated Oritech factory."
			]
