		{
			dependencies: ["E01D"]
			description: [
				"The §eExo Armour§r set is Oritech's powered endgame armour with modular upgrade slots."
				""
				"§7Pieces:§r Exo Helmet, Exo Chestplate, Exo Leggings, Exo Boots. Each piece accepts §eAugments§r via the §eAugmentation Centre§r."
				""
				"§7Upgrades available:§r Night Vision, Speed Boost, High Jump, Fall Negation, Damage Reduction, Auto-Repair, and more \u2014 each slot stackable with the right augments."
				""
				"§6Bonus:§r The §eExo Jetpack§r (chestplate variant) grants continuous powered flight with no fuel required once charged."
