		{
			dependencies: ["E01E"]
			description: [
				"The §eNuclear Reactor Control Panel§r manages Oritech's multiblock fission reactor \u2014 the pack's most powerful single power source."
				""
				"§7Build sequence:§r"
				"1. Construct a 3\u00d73\u00d73 hollow shell from §eReactor Walls§r"
				"2. Place §eFuel Rods§r inside using Uranium Pellets"
				"3. Add §eReactor Vents§r on the outer faces for heat dissipation"
				"4. Place the §eControl Panel§r on any outer face"
				"5. Connect an §eEnergy Port§r to your power network"
				"6. Insert fuel rods, then start the reactor from the Control Panel"
				""
				"§cWarning:§r Monitor the heat meter. Without sufficient vents, overheating causes an explosion. Always match vent count to fuel rod count."
			]
